我這裡是在pi上裝svn直接裝：
1.sudo apt-get install subversion

接著把最新版的streamer抓下來(pi做這件事情會有點小慢)
2.sudo svn co https://svn.code.sf.net/p/mjpg-streamer/code/ mjpg-streamer

3.sudo apt-get install libjpeg8-dev imagemagick

4.cd mjpg-streamer;sudo make
4.1 : videodev.h : No such file -> sudo ln -s /usr/include/linux/videodev2.h /usr/include/linux/videodev.h

5:./mjpg_streamer -i “./input_uvc.so" -o “./output_http.so -w ./www"
5.1:./mjpgstreamer -i "./inputuvc.so -d /dev/video0 -n -y f 15 -r 640x480" -o "./output_http.so /www"
